(7)

Where fit is the appearance embedding of the current matched observation, Œ± = 0.9 is a momentum term. Finally observations that are not assigned to any tracklets are initialized as new tracklets if they consecutively appear in 2 frames. A tracklet is terminated if it is not updated in the most current 30 frames.
Note this association method is simpler than the cascade matching strategy proposed in SORT [3], since we only apply association once for one frame and resort to a buÔ¨Äer pool to deal with those shortly lost tracklets. Moreover, we also

